Re: Resending transaction

Bitcointalk

2010-07-16 15:01:33 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Bitcoin automatically rebroadcasts your transactions if it receives new
   blocks that donʼt contain them.  It may take about an hour to get
   rebroadcasted.  It is relentless though.  It will keep nagging the
   network forever until your transaction gets into a block.
